article.headline: IPFW 63, Valparaiso 46
article.story: VALPARAISO, Ind. -- David Carson had 16 points and nine rebounds as IPFW defeated Valparaiso 63-46 on Wednesday night. Deilvez Yearby had 13 points and eight rebounds, Nick Daniels scored 13 points and Zach Plackemeier added nine points and five assists for the Mastodons (4-5), who never trailed. Howard Little led Valparaiso (3-5) with 11 points, but none of his teammates scored in double figures. Jake Diebler and Michael Rogers each scored eight points for the Crusaders. IPFW held Valparaiso to 31 percent shooting overall, including 4-for-21 shooting from 3-point range. IPFW led 31-18 at halftime after shooting 48 percent in the first 20 minutes. The Mastodons led by as many as 23 points in the second half. The Mastodons outrebounded the Crusaders 41-31.
